com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.elements

Class ViewElementBuilderContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.elements.ViewElementBuilderContext

  • public class ViewElementBuilderContext
extends Object
    Represents the builder context in which ViewElement instances should be constructed. Typically a context is represented by:
    • the EntityConfiguration of the entity that is holding the values
    • the EntityPropertyRegistry providing access to the different property descriptors
    • the EntityMessageCodeResolver that should be used for resolving messages
    • the mode for which the view elements should be created
    • the EntityFormService that created this context and can be used to retrieve builders
    See Also:
    EntityFormService, ViewElementBuilder
